程序包 io.github.moyusowo.neoartisanapi.api.block.state

接口 ArtisanCropState

所有超级接口:
ArtisanBaseBlockState
@NonExtendable public interface ArtisanCropState extends ArtisanBaseBlockState
Crop block state definition.

Crop-type blocks that break when pushed by pistons, cannot float in air, and can be washed away by water.
